snippet.title: The Cleaner - TRAILER 2 - A John Wick, Superhot and Hotline Miami inspired game
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1389020/The_Cleaner/
Twitter : https://twitter.com/DystopiaCorp

The Cleaner is a hardcore die 'n' retry inspired by John Wick, Hotline Miami and SuperHot. You control a highly-trained " cleaner " with a unique power. No cliché storyline, no cutscenes, start the game and play.
